Sum of Even Numbers: Write a Python program to find the sum of all even numbers from 1 to 100.
Fibonacci Sequence: Generate the first N Fibonacci numbers, where N is input by the user.
Prime Number Checker: Write a function to check whether a number is prime or not.
Palindrome Checker: Write a program that takes a string and checks whether it is a palindrome (reads the same forward and backward).
List Reversal: Given a list of numbers, reverse the list without using the built-in reverse function.
Factorial of a Number: Write a function to calculate the factorial of a number using recursion.